<h2>Our Story</h2>

<p>
	Established 2013.
</p>
<p>

	Born in the corner of a crowded room and fueled by a steady diet of fuzz pedals and caffeine, Bristling Bangers has been keeping the vinyl tradition alive since 2013. We aren’t just a record shop; we’re a community hub for the sonically obsessed, the late-night crate diggers, and anyone who believes music sounds better when it’s pressed into wax.
</p>
<p>
	For over a decade, we’ve curated a meticulously selected wall of records, but our true passion lies in the underground. As an independent publisher, we dedicate our lives to championing alternative and indie bands who deserve to be heard. We don't just sell the culture—we help build it.
</p>
<p>
	Whether you’re hunting for a rare original press, looking to discover your new favorite indie outfit, or just want to argue about track listings, our doors are always open. Drop in, drop the needle, and get bristling.
</p>

